description:
This Badge is for people who are active in the 𝓐𝓨𝓐 𝓑𝓪𝓭𝓰𝓮𝓻 𝓒𝓵𝓪𝓷. (You can earn this too).

𝐄𝐚𝐫𝐧 𝐮𝐩 𝐭𝐨 𝟏𝟎𝟎% 𝐃𝐢𝐬𝐜𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐭!

With this Badge you also receive <𝓐𝓬𝓽𝓲𝓿𝓮 𝓑𝓪𝓭𝓰𝓮𝓻> 'rank'  in Discord so people will know they've got backup.

If you are active you will get spotted by our moderators. They will approach you.

What does active mean?
-Help others;
-Amount of XP (earned by badges in our Space);
-Join Discord;
-Follow Twitter;
-Retweet;
-Replying (to someone in the community);
-Win awards & rewards;
-Buy art;
-Donate;
-Share idea's in discord;
-Share (AYA) nature art; 
-Bring in new members;
-Your own initiative to help the community

Extra pointer: The more XP you have (in the AYA Space) the more discount you receive.

